   'Situation: I was passed over for a small promotion at my place of work. The person who got the promotion was younger and less experienced than me, but a favorite of the boss.\nDistorted Thought: I was angry because I was the better person for the job.\nRational Response: My emotional reactions to not getting something I want are valid and I can decide how to respond next from a rational place',
