   "Situation: I got upset at my boss for not putting me in a temporary promotion to act as supervisor of our team.\nDistorted Thought: I wasn't valued as much as the other person.\nRational Response: The promotion is temporary. Maybe my boss wants to promote me to a permanent position instead. I am still a good employee and maybe my promotion will come later.",
   "Situation: An mturk requester rejected my task and I wasn't sure why because I work very hard on my tasks. Being new it affected my approval rating more negatively.\nDistorted Thought: I'm not smart enough to succeed at mturk\nRational Response: I am learning still and can improve. Just because this one task did not go as well as I would like does not mean I cannot improve and do better in the future.",
