   'Situation: Last week, my co-worker was invited to participate in a workshop and I was not.\nDistorted Thought: My co-worker is better than me.\nRational Response: There are many reasons why I was not invited to participate in a workshop, one of which may be that my company does not feel I need training on this topic.',
