   'Situation: I have been studying for months for the real estate exam. When I went to take it, I did not pass by two points.\nDistorted Thought: I really have to pass, I need to work.\nRational Response: I can retake the exam. I have prepared for it, and now I can be more prepared to take it in the future.',
