   "Situation: The guy I'm dating went home early one night and I got upset because I thought it meant he didn't want to see me anymore, but I was wrong.\nDistorted Thought: I guess he doesn't like me anymore\nRational Response: I will reach out to him to discuss how he's been feeling, I cannot know what he is thinking or feeling.",
