   'Situation: i dont wanna continue with this life\nDistorted Thought: im ready to die\nRational Response: I want to live',
   "Situation: I hate my life\nDistorted Thought: Killing myself\nRational Response: I've been having a lot of bad days lately. But even if I don't remember the good days, I know I've had them. And if I've had good days before, I can have good days again.",
   "Situation: Depression that started 3 years ago\nDistorted Thought: Suicidal thoughts\nRational Response: I'm having a hard time, but at least I'm taking steps to feel better by learning more about mental health and reaching out for help.",
