   "Situation: They are racist\nDistorted Thought: I hate Republicans\nRational Response: There are lots of things in the world I'd like to change. I can focus on what I can control and do my best to make a difference",
   "Situation: My friends don't help me when I ask them to help with my suicidal thoughts.\nDistorted Thought: I want to end my life.\nRational Response: I'm having a hard time getting the help I need. I can try reaching out to someone new or calling a helpline. Asking for help is hard, but I know I can do it.",
