   "Situation: I feel that I do not deserve the people I love, and that they probably aren’t as happy to see me as they let on.\nDistorted Thought: I’ve been recently diagnosed with diabetes, I’m overweight, I hate how I look, and my crush probably does not like me in the same way, and I feel incredibly inferior to others when I think about her.\nRational Response: I don't know for sure how my crush feels about me until I ask her. People of all shapes and sizes find love all the time.",
