   "Situation: My boyfriend told me that I shouldn't clean the bathroom and to go and deal with the kids.\nDistorted Thought: He doesn't think that I'm capable of watching the kids and cleaning the kitchen at the same time.\nRational Response: I have a lot going on. I can ask my boyfriend to help me with one of the tasks.",
